 \u00faltima instancia, el camino m\u00e1s sabio es estar abierto a cualquier m\u00e9todo eficaz de curaci\u00f3n, al margen de su car\u00e1cter alop\u00e1tico u holista. Cualquier tratamiento capaz de potenciar su curaci\u00f3n, devolverle la esperanza y hacer que su cuerpo recupere la salud merece tenerse en cuenta.\u201d Caroline Myss.", "language": null, "image": "https://www.naturarespira.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/medicina-holistica-y-alopatica.jpg", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["https://www.naturarespira.com", "#", "#", "#", "#", "https://www.naturarespira.com/", null, "https://www.naturarespira.com/profesor-de-respiracion/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/testimonios/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/departamento-id/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/natura-en-el-mundo/", "https://tienda.naturarespira.com/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/naturaverso/", null, "https://www.naturarespira.com/terapia-individual/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/curso-de-respiracion-el-arte-de-vivir/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/curso-de-respiracion-consciente/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/coach-de-respiracion/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/noticias/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/blog-curso-de-respiracion/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/contacto-curso-de-respiracion/", "https://academia.naturarespira.com/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/", null, "https://www.naturarespira.com/profesor-de-respiracion/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/testimonios/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/departamento-id/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/natura-en-el-mundo/", "https://tienda.naturarespira.com/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/naturaverso/", null, "https://www.naturarespira.com/terapia-individual/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/curso-de-respiracion-el-arte-de-vivir/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/curso-de-respiracion-consciente/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/coach-de-respiracion/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/noticias/", "https://www.naturarespira.com/blog-